snippet.textDisplay: Piya Calling from France✨️ This song touches me deeply and would resonate with many others, especially in these troubled times in France. Thank you for reminding us of the strength of cultural diversity. This song gave hope that nothing can erase the love between the country 🇨🇵 where you grew up and your country of origin 🇵🇰.
